text: Eve Myles (born 26 July 1978 in Ystradgynlais, Powys), is a Welsh actress. She is most known for playing lead characters in Belonging and Doctor Who spin-off series Torchwood. ==Other websites== * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Welsh movie actors Category:Welsh stage actors Category:Welsh television actors Category:Welsh voice actors
